{
  "stem": "2170.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, also we heard closer to us, which was the name of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In the center, in this [INAUDIBLE] is the section of Vinnitsa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Vinnitsa was the main city, like the state.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Of all the small cities near Vinnitsa, they did with the Jews the same thing, like in Mogilev and near Kiev and Babi Yar.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we had a feeling that something is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But nobody told us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Nobody said anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "A week before, couple-- not a week, actually, a couple days before of Christmas, the Germans, whoever-- there were Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They used to call them [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This was boarder guard German soldiers, and the SS and Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A night before of Christmas, they were celebrating, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "At the time before Christmas-- a week or two-- they told all the Jewish people to put on a Star of David, a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Everybody has to wear a star in the front and in the back, so they can recognize the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They also told the Ukrainians if the Jewish people lived in the same house where Ukrainians live-- a Christian-- they should put there a cross on their door, and the Jews a Star of David on their door.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this was the beginning of preparation-- what is going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My sister still worked over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And one night, she mentioned-- she said something is going on, and they're talking about us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Something is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They did not tell her what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the headquarters, this was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A night before Christmas, the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Under us were living Christian people, Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were drinking the whole night.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
